> ::Composer/Orchestra::
> 
>        Composer nods, then looks at Wheeljack.  
> 
>         "Say, is there a layout of the base and the island?  If I 
could study it, I may be able to improve our defenses," He asked.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
>         Orchestra gets a smile on his face.
> 
>         "Ya!  We're the Predacons!" He says with his pride and 
glory.
>

my chip?  I mean, it's just that I want to be a full Predacon with no 
flaws in my Predacon status," He asked.
